"title": "5857: fame",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5857: fame",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The reputation gained by individuals or groups of people as a result of their achievements. Scripture shows how God's fame among the nations rested upon his saving actions and, in the NT, how the miracles of Jesus Christ brought him widespread fame. God's people are to rejoice in his fame, without lapsing into arrogance.</p>\n<h2>God's acts of salvation have brought him renown</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:9-Josh9:10\">JOS 9:9–9:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:9-Exod8:11\">EXO 8:9–8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:13-Num14:16\">NUM 14:13–14:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:1-Ps72:19\">PSA 72:1–72:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:13-Ps135:14\">PSA 135:13–135:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:13\">ISA 55:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:11-Isa63:14\">ISA 63:11–63:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:20\">JER 32:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:2\">HAB 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's teaching and miracles brought him fame</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:24\">MAT 4:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:32-Matt8:34\">MAT 8:32–8:34</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:14-Mark5:17\">MRK 5:14–5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:34-Luke8:37\">LUK 8:34–8:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27-Matt9:31\">MAT 9:27–9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:27-Mark1:28\">MRK 1:27–1:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:36-Luke4:37\">LUK 4:36–4:37</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ taught servanthood rather than the pursuit of status and fame</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:33-Mark9:35\">MRK 9:33–9:35</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:1-Matt18:4\">MAT 18:1–18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:46-Luke9:48\">LUK 9:46–9:48</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:42-Mark10:45\">MRK 10:42–10:45</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:25-Matt20:28\">MAT 20:25–20:28</a></p>\n<h2>Israel's fame dependent on her obedience to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:18-Deut26:19\">DEU 26:18–26:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:24-Deut2:25\">DEU 2:24–2:25</a></p>\n<h3>Israel made famous in order to glorify God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:11\">JER 13:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:9\">JER 33:9</a></p>\n<h3>Israel's abuse of her fame led to judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:14-Ezek16:15\">EZK 16:14–16:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:35-Ezek16:42\">EZK 16:35–16:42</a></p>\n<h3>Glorious restoration promised by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:7\">HOS 14:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:4\">ISA 61:1–61:4</a></p>\n<h2>Local, national or international fame</h2>\n<h3>Local</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:30\">1CH 12:30</a></strong></p>\n<h3>National</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:27\">JOS 6:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:4\">EST 9:4</a></p>\n<h3>International</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:17\">1CH 14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:31\">1KI 4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:1\">1KI 10:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:1\">2CH 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:8\">2CH 26:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:1-Isa45:7\">ISA 45:1–45:7</a></p>\n<h2>God's judgment on the arrogance that may come with fame</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:8-Isa23:9\">ISA 23:8–23:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:16-Jer48:18\">JER 48:16–48:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:29-Jer48:30\">JER 48:29–48:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:15-Ezek26:18\">EZK 26:15–26:18</a></p>\n<h2>Famous for doing wrong</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:40\">NUM 16:40</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:34\">1KI 15:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:11\">JUD 1:11</a></p>",
